column5: Got a couple skis Saturday morning...  The one in the second pic is the one that started the first aid kit thread...
I'd be happy with a couple of those
those are some really nice fish!..
Nice fish. I am severe slime withdrawal.

Keep posting pics like these.  I'm drooling over them.  Just saying that I'm looking at them in Colorado and if I even got a whiff of anybody looking to go to St Lawrence, I certainly would recommend Musky Mike as their guide.  I know that I would enjoy fishing with you.  Seem cool and always on fish.  Good luck in your endeavors.  Slayer8
Haven't boated a ski yet this year, although I haven't honestly fished for them either, lol.  Good job Mike.
Nice pair of 'skis!!! I'm hoping to hook one or two next week.
